data.description: Immerse yourself in the meticulously maintained charm of this townhouse nestled within the sought-after Piney Orchard Community. Upon entering through the front door, the foyer welcomes you into the expansive open-concept kitchen, dining and living room. The main level boasts a well-appointed kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a convenient powder room. Delight in the appeal of vinyl plank flooring, crown molding, recessed lighting, and an overflow of natural light enveloping the area.  Ascend to the upper level to discover two generously sized bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a separate laundry room for added convenience. The crown jewel is the top-floor primary suite, spanning the entirety of the home. Enjoy the spaciousness, abundant natural light, a cozy gas fireplace, and a walk-in closet. The recently renovated luxurious primary ensuite bathroom features a glass-enclosed shower, double vanity, and a soaking tub.  Step out onto the appealing patio and discover a separate storage shed, rounding out the exterior amenities of this home. Seize the opportunity to reside in one of Anne Arundel County’s premier communities, boasting amenities such as outdoor and indoor swimming pools, a Community Center with an exercise room, a picturesque lake with walking paths, jogging/cycling trails, tennis courts, playgrounds, and more!  Convenience is paramount, with close proximity to Ft. Meade, Baltimore, MARC train, trendy restaurants, and numerous shopping options. Don't miss out on this exceptional home– schedule a showing today!
